  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "12. tenth day—But in 2Ki 25:8, it is said \"the seventh day.\" Nebuzara-dan started from Riblah on the \"seventh\" day and arrived in Jerusalem on the \"tenth\" day. Seeming discrepancies, when cleared up, confirm the genuineness of Scripture; for they show there was no collusion between the writers; as in all God's works there is latent harmony under outward varieties.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
